Generic single-database configuration for IPAM System.

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for managing database schema changes.

## Usage

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback migrations
```bash
alembic downgrade -1  # Rollback one migration
alembic downgrade <revision>  # Rollback to specific revision
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
alembic current
```

## Notes

- The env.py file is configured to automatically import all models from app.models
- Database URL is loaded from app.core.config.settings
- All migrations are stored in the versions/ directory
